  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "クリスマスに女の子に愛の告白をさせることを目指す恋愛シミュレーションゲームです。ゲームの目的は、クリスマスの日に女の子に愛の告白をさせ、完璧なデートを計画する手助けをすることです。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "A bishoujo game for the Game Boy by KID Corp. in 1997.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Hero's love interest is in the higher grade class. This year he gets in the same class with his childhood friend and she piques his interest a lot as well. He is not confident in his abilities, but this year he wants to find his love. Hopefully by Christmas...",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
